Author: comicsansmasterfont
Text: I never thought about it but it depends on my mindset I guess? When I’m full-blown restriction mode I’m like “it’s not a real fast until it hits 382682 hours, you pansy; your organs haven’t even shut down and you still have hair lol get serious pls”. But when I’m bingeing it’s more like “just completed 4 minutes fasting, I truly am the skinniest goddess that ever walked this earth, we getting that autophagy bitch”
